    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >大家好！我是留老太:D。醉风酒是一款什么游戏呢？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >小时候，你在父母的餐馆里长大，生活说不上奢侈，却也无忧无虑。突然有一天，餐馆被人陷害，父母也相继去世，你只能靠打工维持生计。原以为日子会一直这样过下去，直到有一天，久别重逢的青梅突然出现，并背负了100万贷款？！你的命运就此改写。沉寂的醉风酒即将迎来新的曙光，然而，过去的阴霾并未完全消散……</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >背负重担，与伙伴一起前行！在重振家业的同时，你能找到真相吗？</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>请看！🌟主要玩法🌟</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >作为餐馆老板，最重要的当然是指定餐馆的经营策略。你可以选定餐馆每月的菜谱，决定每道菜品的价格，决定是否装修和扩建店铺，是给顾客提供上乘的服务，还是压低成本来得到收入呢，是投入大量金钱培训员工，又或者开两千的月薪，90小时的工时呢。这些————都由你决定！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >当然，最重要的要存活下来。如果连续两个月现金为负数————欢迎来到破产的be结局^^</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3222890/extras/c1fe623de501b29b7a2aa00bace4e2c5.avif?t=1768521589\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3222890/extras_big/c1fe623de501b29b7a2aa00bace4e2c5.avif?t=1768521589 width=1560 height=870 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >🌟丰富而有趣的小游戏🌟</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >料理、打扫清洁、检查账单错误、处理客户问题.......每天从清晨6点到夜晚10点，都有好多工作要做！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >来体验每日的经营日常吧！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3222890/extras/96459138680bb5e30a0bc02916e85c2d.avif?t=1768521589\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3222890/extras_big/96459138680bb5e30a0bc02916e85c2d.avif?t=1768521589 width=1560 height=874 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>🌟贴贴？学习？逛庙会？享受石头镇的日常吧🌟</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >救你于水火的青梅、从小一起四处闯祸的竹马、来历成谜脾气火爆的少女……小小醉风酒聚集了众多性格各异的角色，了解他/她们的过往故事，贴贴来增加好感度吧。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >事业脑表示，不要贴贴，我要学习！在醉风酒里，你也可以和员工学习他/她们专属的知识。想知道什么是翻台率？菜单上的注意力小心机你有注意到吗？切菜先选刀，炒蔬菜为什么经常最后才加盐？如何判断鸡蛋是否还可以实用？还有肯波流空手道、八字和紫微星盘的算命占卜......如果你对这些感兴趣，不妨多跟员工们聊天学习吧！知识不仅是数值，也是真正有用的小技巧，和结局的分支之一哦。<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3222890/extras/a15ead83a08f4e79c6b98cd6e1a289b3.avif?t=1768521589\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3222890/extras_big/a15ead83a08f4e79c6b98cd6e1a289b3.avif?t=1768521589 width=800 height=448 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3222890/extras/44166d933449ad96aad6e14a84f12222.poster.avif?t=1768521589\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3222890/extras/44166d933449ad96aad6e14a84f12222.webm?t=1768521589\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3222890/extras/44166d933449ad96aad6e14a84f12222.mp4?t=1768521589\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3222890/extras/077a16b4489a6fc0c330ee704d5020aa.avif?t=1768521589\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3222890/extras_big/077a16b4489a6fc0c330ee704d5020aa.avif?t=1768521589 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>🌟超多cg的丰富结局？🌟</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在醉风酒里，虽然有5年内还清一百万贷款的目标，但是你的选择都会指向不同的结局。是做压榨员工但盆满钵满的老板还是选择有良心？是选择连锁店策略积极扩张、开大酒楼，还是米其林饭店？又或许...即便餐馆是主业，却沉迷投资、钓鱼和赌博？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >而这些，都会引向属于你的独特的结局。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3222890/extras/28bbf79ce74685facbbc628a36f1ef00.avif?t=1768521589\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3222890/extras_big/28bbf79ce74685facbbc628a36f1ef00.avif?t=1768521589 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
